{"tid":1253351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"留意到政府同TVB不停想分化年輕人同老一輩既人，大家係時候諗諗計反擊","createTime":"2019-06-23T13:55:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T06:00:06.000Z","uid":203019,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"377b66fef8933a1fd2f228cb1654158bce51cdc8","tid":1253351,"uid":203019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:55:01.000Z","msg":"今日係FB見到好多人分享「致年青人：沒有上街的父母根本沒愛過你」呢段片，段片動機只有一個，就係分化年輕人同老一輩既人。<br />\n<br />\n除左呢段片，TVB平時好鍾意搵老一輩去做訪問，多數播出街嘅片都係呢班話班後生仔唔和平，搞亂民生等，經常營造出老一輩同後生仔對立的情況。好多人睇完新聞，潛移默化加上同輩效應，好易會被影響，最終就會變成年輕人同大人永遠無法站左同一陣線。<br />\n<br />\n發夢見到，其實除左遊行，612都有好多「大人」有走出黎，當然，無可否認走在最前線多數係後生仔。621佔警總，我都夢見有好多「大人」，企我身邊個大人仲要俾捉鬼隊以為係警察，其後佢有好大聲幫手嗌口號。<br />\n<br />\n我地係唔係都應該拍下片，整下街訪，問下「大人」對呢一兩星期睇法，用「大人」的角度，去講出大家的心聲，然後再share出去俾更多人睇，將大人同後生仔拉返埋一齊？大家有冇更好方法可以宣傳同反擊？(之前FB瘋傳RTHK有個錄音講3個大人嘅睇法，都非常大迴響)"},{"pid":"8b97f8c7d3b15376562bb871c7c900a6800ef00a","tid":1253351,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:58:54.000Z","msg":"聽日煲底聚集 完唔好去嗰啲政府部門， 直接去有落廣告嗰啲 商舖， 一齊過去幫佢哋宣傳下?"},{"pid":"646aaeb5ede5b37f828d3b8fc58b787ba5d92d51","tid":1253351,"uid":156130,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:59:37.000Z","msg":"條片擺明係建制做出嚟明屈"},{"pid":"7f666307049d675f200a4d14d010402093f3a83a","tid":1253351,"uid":203019,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"646aaeb5ede5b37f828d3b8fc58b787ba5d92d51","tid":1253351,"uid":156130,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:59:37.000Z","msg":"條片擺明係建制做出嚟明屈"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:00:43.000Z","msg":"諗條片個人好高招，成功分化唔少人"},{"pid":"4c6d791180445c90e5495a14746b84c3fd2ceaf6","tid":1253351,"uid":50457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:07:40.000Z","msg":"而家要反攻，年青人成年人同一陣線抗共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人本著良知，同心抗共"},{"pid":"b38e8f06c1a42a98b480eb25617cd248632985f1","tid":1253351,"uid":203019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:15:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9a704b69651ba7c15ca5bb5e95f2e14a8a406757","tid":1253351,"uid":54528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:17:29.000Z","msg":"搞到今時今日咁 上一代既人, 上左岸既人都要負責任<br />\n唔係咩野都係馬照跑舞照跳架<br />\n仲唔醒覺既廢老藍絲, 無得救"},{"pid":"664dbf114866f1294ad661318929d5b1c4ea2546","tid":1253351,"uid":192409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:19:07.000Z","msg":"大家都係香港人 大家都要反送中 守護香港, 一睇呢種分化片就知係5毛作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098913912b1eda435c03f389357dab3879f6ee40","tid":1253351,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:25:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e4975aea04aae99e253972a682360b31a5314c","tid":1253351,"uid":203019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a17ba44f3a2b132683f7966176d419bd4028d17","tid":1253351,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:29:53.000Z","msg":"[齊cut TVB] 如果我裝Cable，tag兩位朋友叫佢地裝Cable/Now，有無得諗？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1253364\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1253364</a>"},{"pid":"e6f8faee1303022fd82948ef8999bb2c187a5919","tid":1253351,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f666307049d675f200a4d14d010402093f3a83a","tid":1253351,"uid":203019,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"646aaeb5ede5b37f828d3b8fc58b787ba5d92d51","tid":1253351,"uid":156130,"like":3,"